Package: Smoodjustment
Type: Package
Title: Adjust a smoothed raster so that its volume matches original unsmoothed
  raster
Version: 0.0.9999
Author: c(person("Marko", "Kallio", email = "marko@markokallio.fi", 
                  role = c("aut", "cre"), 
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6917-7790"))
Maintainer: Marko Kallio <marko@markokallio.fi>
Description: Adjust a smoothed raster so that its volume matches original 
  unsmoothed raster. Smoodjustment does this by smoothing the difference in 
  rasters by Tobler's pycnophylactic interpolation.
